“Libre Software Engineering", at http://libresoft.urjc.es/, is '''a research project that looks in the technical processes and management of such projects'''. They have a research blog, at http://libresoft.urjc.es:9080/libresoft , and keep  track of research developments through Research Planet, at http://libresoft.urjc.es/planet/ 

FlossWorld is a study on the worldwide development and use of FLOSS software, at http://www.flossworld.org/ 

